Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，早飯做好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.80,0:01:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.03,0:01:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼，是年曆嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.81,0:01:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.54,0:01:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.58,0:02:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，是撫子\N還在做模特兒工作的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個可以給我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.92,0:02:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了，謝謝爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早餐做好了\N快點下來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.17,0:02:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.54,0:02:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第54話 小櫻與回憶的年曆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊\N那是媽媽的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年曆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上我在整理東西時找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（藤隆的生日）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（桃矢的生日）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.25,0:03:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連哥哥的生日也有寫上耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.85,0:03:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生日會寫在年曆\N可是4年才一次喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.02,0:03:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有記的年份\N撫子也都會用大字加上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（小櫻的生日）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連我的生日也寫上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.58,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早\N早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早，知世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.03,0:03:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼好事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得出來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很了解妳嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸說這是媽媽用過的年曆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.61,0:04:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年曆這種東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前是畫在地上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.69,0:04:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是寫在土上的話\N風一吹、一下雨就不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.12,0:04:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有貓或狗走過\N又會留下腳印看不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以很麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.46,0:04:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此為了防止年曆消失\N就出現了叫作“年曆監視員”的行業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又在吹牛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.41,0:04:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他的想像力真的好豐富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早\N早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.12,0:04:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.12,0:04:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柊澤，關於年曆的歷史\N你也聽說過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.23,0:05:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，柊澤跟你不同\N他是很認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂得還真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.97,0:05:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古代的歐洲，年曆監視員\N曾是大家嚮往的行業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.57,0:05:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以惡作劇破壞年曆的人\N會遭到嚴厲的處分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.55,0:05:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，在歷史上也記載了\N許多關於年曆的事件及爭執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.05,0:05:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最有名的應該是關於被寫在埃及\N長達100公里年曆的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.66,0:05:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是外星人的傑作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.63,0:05:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你似乎能合得來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得應該不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.11,0:05:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來柊澤跟山崎\N是同一型的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.25,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前的人真辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起彈彈看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈得很好，桃矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈得真好，桃矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽過這首曲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我媽作的曲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美的曲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桃矢，你還會彈琴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.96,0:09:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月城，弓箭社的社長在叫你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像又要你去幫忙參加比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.60,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳\N那我先走了喔，桃矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.70,0:09:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的寫了好多事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.87,0:09:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是工作吧\N還有哥哥的教學觀摩日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.28,0:09:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是知世媽媽的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.46,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是早一點知道\N我就能準備禮物了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要記下來，明年送她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（爺爺的生日）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.07,0:10:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…\N是媽媽的爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.27,0:10:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說是我的曾祖父囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.31,0:10:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾祖父是什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了\N妳回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是曾祖父的生日耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（藤隆負責晚餐桃矢打工）\N（小櫻清理飯後餐桌）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.01,0:10:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽都會送禮物給曾祖父吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.88,0:11:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為撫子的禮物\N總是親手做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.86,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是媽媽不會做菜\N也不會做裁縫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.19,0:11:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，不過撫子總是很努力的做著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那現在曾祖父呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.47,0:11:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很健康啊\N但我只見過他一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.27,0:11:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.57,0:11:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為曾祖父非常疼撫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他認為我是把他最疼愛的撫子\N搶走的壞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.15,0:11:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸才不是壞人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.79,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然…雖然我不記得媽媽的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.43,0:11:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是照片上的媽媽\N看起來總是很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果沒有爸爸跟媽媽\N就不會生下我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.54,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好幸福喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（爺爺的生日）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不可以送禮物給曾祖父？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.86,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想像媽媽一樣\N親手做禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做的大概不行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.23,0:12:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N現在才準備或許來不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.37,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要努力的做\N到晚上應該做得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.18,0:12:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒辦法在今天送過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.58,0:12:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心\N有個人可以確實交給他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.32,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾祖父一定會很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊，接下來再縫這裡跟這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.23,0:13:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.48,0:13:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了，做好了，做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.72,0:13:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，媽媽都怎麼送禮物的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.03,0:13:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禮物上附上信跟瞿麥花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.23,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花店已經關了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.77,0:14:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.14,0:14:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快彈風琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是曾祖父的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.05,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去彈上次媽媽作的曲子\N把它用錄音帶錄下來，馬上喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就幫她彈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.10,0:14:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此，所以她今天才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.37,0:14:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可，小可\N你在玩什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要變花出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾祖父的生日啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你也說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.92,0:14:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是真正必要的時候\N不可以使用小櫻牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.53,0:15:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能使用魔法變出花來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的想變出花來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.44,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就試試看吧\N只要妳是真心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想魔法應該不會失控的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘊藏星星力量的鑰匙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.96,0:15:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯現真正的神力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.16,0:15:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據契約，小櫻命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除封印！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「花」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓曾祖父了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.55,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸跟媽媽還有哥哥\N以及我都非常幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.66,0:16:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然敢找我出來\N真是大膽啊，老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.93,0:16:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是爺爺的生日是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.97,0:16:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撫子每年都會送生日禮物給爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是做得很好的親手禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.18,0:17:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫著自己嫁給\N木之本老師後有多幸福的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.99,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及瞿麥花…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.92,0:17:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是小櫻特別做的\N我一定會在今天送去給爺爺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.20,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，只要知世的媽媽送去\N就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.61,0:17:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能讓曾祖父高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（藤隆休假，桃矢打工）\N（小櫻沒社團活動，在家幫爸爸）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，這裡是木之本家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.83,0:17:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,園美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真的很謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.54,0:18:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻也很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？爺爺他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.70,0:18:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，真抱歉突然將你找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.65,0:18:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們多久沒見面了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.02,0:18:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從我與撫子\N送結婚邀請函的那天到現在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.60,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了園美送來的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.01,0:19:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信上面努力地寫著\N撫子有多麼的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.41,0:19:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及小櫻現在有多麼幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.68,0:19:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請將這個交給小櫻與桃矢好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.75,0:19:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我的回禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.69,0:19:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.43,0:19:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.14,0:19:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直有話想對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.98,0:19:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.72,0:20:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我知道\N你是撫子選的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.13,0:20:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以帶給她幸福\N但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.37,0:20:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時撫子才16歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.68,0:20:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我是個新上任的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.52,0:20:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道日後會讓她有多辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.32,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓自己疼愛的孫女\N跟那種人在一起，這是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.86,0:20:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我只是在意氣用事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.33,0:20:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子嫁人以後\N我就很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.71,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我有告訴撫子就好了\N說她真的選了個好男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.75,0:21:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的孫女是全世界最幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.73,0:21:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定正在某個地方聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.03,0:21:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.66,0:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是曾祖父給妳跟桃矢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.50,0:21:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說謝謝你們送的生日禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.90,0:21:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾祖父來過了嗎？\N他在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.04,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，這是他派人送來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.58,0:21:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.81,0:22:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他似乎很高興\N太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以打開嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.78,0:22:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了，妳的禮物是下面那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.46,0:22:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿穿看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.03,0:22:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.44,0:22:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.78,0:22:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是上次去別墅時\N收到的衣服嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.12,0:22:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只把我彈開\N竟然還不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.63,0:22:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.70,0:22:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾祖父不知道了解了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.07,0:23:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽跟我們都很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.74,0:23:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.18,0:23:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天，我會見到曾祖父吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.25,0:23:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.39,0:23:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對，媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.23,0:24:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡究竟是哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.47,0:24:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒看過這個景色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.44,0:24:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而艾瑞爾居然變成貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.01,0:24:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個景色好像跟\N剛才看的書裡的插圖很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.78,0:24:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛魔法使\N「小櫻與不可思議王國的小櫻」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.52,0:24:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也與小櫻一起\N解除封印！
